{"tid":2462173,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"試過斷捨離/大清屋既你入黎傾下計","createTime":"2021-03-26T00:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T03:33:11.000Z","uid":180913,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ee528ff2d2a3669525a20ea7506025a8d29b28b8","tid":2462173,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:16:01.000Z","msg":"入黎吹下水，發覺執野過程都有唔少回億，好多時拎到上手都唔捨得扔。<br />\n開個post交流下d樣有效清屋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我斷捨離嘅原因係想多d空間同想扔去唔好回憶。<br />\n是咁的<br />\n上年經歷俾人屈陷害名譽掃地同埋金錢都有損失之後意志清沉。<br />\n返返下工唔想再返.<br />\n成個世界封閉哂日日訓起張床度。<br />\n返返下連pt都唔返，人都唔想見，行行下係條街突然無力好緊張企左係度唔想再行。<br />\n有一次試過好難呼吸有d想暈咁，個人愈黎愈倦咁。<br />\n返到屋企之後覺得突然好需要更多空間。總之，想好扔哂d野重新開始。<br />\n<br />\n我自己就冇睇啲咩斷捨離嘅書<br />\n直接行動！<br />\n<br />\n我係好多書雜誌同一個文具控，所以我就第一時間搵到佔位最多物品郁手。<br />\n<br />\n雜誌全扔-每頁都望過一次真係好中意先影低。<br />\n歷史/無用/dse書全扔<br />\n<br />\n文具同紙<br />\n我罰左自己係房一星期多無煩惱咁樣抄字典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計埋螢光筆我有成過千枝筆一星期用哂有d唔靚唔順直接扔。<br />\n<br />\n香水/就快過期爽膚水<br />\n直接倒落去水口<br />\n<br />\n留一件系列<br />\n如果你諗左十秒都唔知幾時再用到，但樣野有番咁上下價值同有機會用到。<br />\n俾自己留一樣做「後備」<br />\n化妝品 唇膏  手套 帽等等<br />\n<br />\n諗都唔洗諗<br />\n過期，衫褲鞋襪覺得鬆同爛咗嘅話即扔<br />\n<br />\n要記住垃圾係歸垃圾桶<br />\n每樣物件都會有吸塵垢係表面<br />\n同班積塵垃圾長期共對影響堆自己就唔好<br />\n佢唔應該知佔有你既空間。<br />\n有時既野緣盡到此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aef91bd7705cfb17d60d67ae36a4418182b46f3","tid":2462173,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:19:29.000Z","msg":"搵到啲野一年以上無用過已經想dump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍唔到手唔dump佢地"},{"pid":"446cbe9e1f40308380e3c579499ab705c37435cb","tid":2462173,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:20:25.000Z","msg":"剩係書同雜誌浪費紙巾賣都40蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有2堆書 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撕紙好治愈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02349fa270bff2467423b73e78ba5e31e9b4572","tid":2462173,"uid":180913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5aef91bd7705cfb17d60d67ae36a4418182b46f3","tid":2462173,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:19:29.000Z","msg":"搵到啲野一年以上無用過已經想dump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍唔到手唔dump佢地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:21:27.000Z","msg":"扔哂佢<br />\n垃圾係應該去垃圾桶<br />\n舊記憶應該刪走再沒留憑證<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddddbfe284d945285280aa2a72cd7261ae8ed0e","tid":2462173,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:22:28.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"dd730b27af3b7456c46218fbd6629087b21250be","tid":2462173,"uid":85252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:22:45.000Z","msg":"方向錯咗<br />\n揀出自己生活必要嘅幾十樣嘢<br />\n其他全扔"},{"pid":"990af14ad82d67e232239ad4a593bfc6dde8551e","tid":2462173,"uid":180913,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd730b27af3b7456c46218fbd6629087b21250be","tid":2462173,"uid":85252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:22:45.000Z","msg":"方向錯咗<br />\n揀出自己生活必要嘅幾十樣嘢<br />\n其他全扔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:24:05.000Z","msg":"錢 男人<br />\n錢 男人 <br />\n錢 男人<br />\n錢 男人<br />\n錢 男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673085985dad07f113a0f497984575cc3fc18f0d","tid":2462173,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-2