021-03-26T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"化妝品我都扔埋 ，留一盒最貴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能因為陪條賤人去買<br />\n我扔得好灑脫。<br />\n<br />\n仲有一招如果係大地色可以做埋眉粉清得快d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔得就加水畫下畫咁<br />\n想清屋既話都要直接扔。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:17:04.000Z","msg":"直接扔左4盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係咪眼影擺得耐上眼會變左唔同色，同埋好難blend<br />\n唇膏都扔左好多，真係唔好信個d beauty youtuber買唇膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本上咀好多色都差不多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留幾支就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n護膚品都係用保濕清潔個類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衫都唔想留多，基本上留1-1.5星期份量既衫乜都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6dd772d566210c7490f61b9387dfa64ce46849","tid":2462173,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e45e2946e154d7676878be9829733946c98f9103","tid":2462173,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2a1b6ed8c3f1a6238f7bae30fa395da1147152","tid":2462173,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"682b827cf58b7da4355d440b69a12c3384ea2b1c","tid":2462173,"uid":32260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:55:29.000Z","msg":"呢個好似叫極簡主義，唔係斷拾離🤔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:00:18.000Z","msg":"原來有分得咁仔細<br />\n我剩係試過大清屋清咗半個月<br />\n扔咗好多好多垃圾<br />\n<br />\n最乞人憎係親戚做成衣<br />\n每年賣剩嗰啲會賤價賣畀「自己人」<br />\n佢就同我哋講話呢件貴嘢嗰件靚嘢<br />\n家母貪平買落根本就件件都係垃圾<br />\n所以先賣剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">扔</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:01:21.000Z","msg":"有無樣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:17:48.000Z","msg":"扔哂就無相喇<br />\n形容下<br />\n1. 明明m碼但膊頭依然過寬<br />\n2. 黑 T-shirt 太厚再印大大張電影海報係正面<br />\n3. 男裝衫 cutting 但有個膊一長一短再加荷葉邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 棕啡色連身衫褲，上邊一撻撻鴨屎綠，著起身成個垃圾婆咁<br />\n5. 淺灰色衫上好多閃片砌個好柒嘅公仔<br />\n6. 條褶裙每瓣直落都有一粒粒波波裝飾，點坐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7. 仲有一大堆過大嘅正常衫<br />\n<br />\n賣剩就總有原因，垃圾就真係不勝枚舉<br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n細個睇中條當季橙紅褶裙<br />\n十分鍾意以為可以等季尾親戚清貨<br />\n屌，當季兩星期已經斷貨啦<br />\n自此就同家母講以後都唔要籮底橙<br />\n然後就一巴摑落來屌咗兩日<br />\n最後係趁佢去旅行清倉扔<br />\n話啲衫畀衣魚啃爛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無相，死無對證"},{"pid":"000727c19bfff43d387bc0cfcbfd1db743038902","tid":2462173,"uid":220922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8f10295aed8b0108247e0e7b5cc21ca1de69f2f","tid":2462173,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:15:46.000Z","msg":"啲書、dvd、衫可以拎去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就咁扔好似好浪費<br />\n有啲仲好新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:18:25.000Z","msg":"捐出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58465a76d35c160c3c42d05de58c3a2ed1aac042","tid":2462173,"uid":220922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a6dd772d566210c7490f61b9387dfa64ce46849","tid":2462173,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e45e2946e154d7676878be9829733946c98f9103","tid":2462173,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2a1b6ed8c3f1a6238f7bae30fa395da1147152","tid":2462173,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:00:18.000Z","msg":"原來有分得咁仔細<br />\n我剩係試過大清屋清咗半個月<br />\n扔咗好多好多垃圾<br />\n<br />\n最乞人憎係親戚做成衣<br />\n每年賣剩嗰啲會賤價賣畀「自己人」<br />\n佢就同我哋講話呢件貴嘢嗰件靚嘢<br />\n家母貪平買落根本就件件都係垃圾<br />\n所以先賣剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><spa